text: Nassarius vanpeli is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Nassariidae, the Nassa mud snails or dog whelks. ==Description== ==Distribution== This species occurs in the Pacific Ocean off the Marquesas. ==References== * Bouchet, P.; Fontaine, B. (2009). List of new marine species described between 2002-2006. Census of Marine Life. Category:Nassariidae Category:Gastropods described in 2005
title: Nassarius vanpeli
